                "Tooltip 在某个点绘制一个浮动的小提示。"),
            "Tooltip.Render(app, 120, 80, \"More information\");");
        IdeDemo.DocAdd(cat, title, body, code, cProj, IdeDemo.T("Project Layout", "项目结构"),
            IdeDemo.T("A project has zan.proj describing the entry file, target platforms, icon and resources. Source files live alongside it.",
                "项目包含 zan.proj，描述入口文件、目标平台、图标和资源。源文件与它放在一起。"),
            "MyApp/\n  zan.proj        // project config (entry, platforms, icon)\n  MyApp.zan       // source / code-behind\n  MyApp.zform     // visual form layout (Window App)\n  assets/         // bundled resources");
